text-gray-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M7 7h10v10\"></path><path d=\"M7 17 17 7\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 text-lg font-semibold\">Eco Friendly</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-gray-500\">Low environmental footprint</p></div></div><div class=\"absolute right-4 bottom-2 z-30\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-60 rounded-[30px] border border-[#ECE7DE] bg-white p-6 shadow-xl\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[#EDF5E9]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trees text-[#2E4B2C]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 10v.2A3 3 0 0 1 8.9 16H5a3 3 0 0 1-1-5.8V10a3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z\"></path><path d=\"M7 16v6\"></path><path d=\"M13 19v3\"></path><path d=\"M12 19h8.3a1 1 0 0 0 .7-1.7L18 14h.3a1 1 0 0 0 .7-1.7L16 9h.2a1 1 0 0 0 .8-1.7L13 3l-1.4 1.5\"></path></svg></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-up-right text-gray-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M7 7h10v10\"></path><path d=\"M7 17 17 7\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 text-lg font-semibold\">Renewable</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-gray-500\">Responsibly harvested jute</p></div></div><div class=\"absolute right-24 top-10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sprout text-[#AFC6A2]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M14 9.536V7a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h1.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5V5a4 4 0 0 1-4 4 4 4 0 0 0-4 4c0 2 1 3 1 5a5 5 0 0 1-1 3\"></path><path d=\"M4 9a5 5 0 0 1 8 4 5 5 0 0 1-8-4\"></path><path d=\"M5 21h14\"></path></svg></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-[#fcfaf7] py-24 lg:py-32\"><div class=\"\n        mx-auto\n        w-full\n        max-w-[1320px]\n        px-5\n        lg:px-8\n        \n      \"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center\"><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-[var(--primary)]\">Our Process</span><h2 class=\"mt-5 font-serif text-5xl text-[var(--text)]\">From Nature To Your Home</h2><p class=\"mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Every NatureGren product follows a thoughtful journey—from natural jute cultivation to handcrafted excellence and premium quality assurance.</p></div><div class=\"mt-20 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-5\"><div class=\"rounded-[28px] border border-[#ece6dc] bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[#edf6e8]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sprout text-[var(--primary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M14 9.536V7a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h1.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5V5a4 4 0 0 1-4 4 4 4 0 0 0-4 4c0 2 1 3 1 5a5 5 0 0 1-1 3\"></path><path d=\"M4 9a5 5 0 0 1 8 4 5 5 0 0 1-8-4\"></path><path d=\"M5 21h14\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Natural Jute</h3><p class=\"mt-4 leading-7 text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Responsibly sourced premium jute fibers are carefully selected.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[28px] border border-[#ece6dc] bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[#edf6e8]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-scissors text-[var(--primary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"3\"></circle><path d=\"M8.12 8.12 12 12\"></path><path d=\"M20 4 8.12 15.88\"></path><circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"18\" r=\"3\"></circle><path d=\"M14.8 14.8 20 20\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Preparation</h3><p class=\"mt-4 leading-7 text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Fibers are cleaned, processed and prepared for handcrafted production.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[28px] border border-[#ece6dc] bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[#edf6e8]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-hand text-[var(--primary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M18 11V6a2 2 0 0 0-2-2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2\"></path><path d=\"M14 10V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M10 10.5V6a2 2 0 0 0-2-2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v8\"></path><path d=\"M18 8a2 2 0 1 1 4 0v6a8 8 0 0 1-8 8h-2c-2.8 0-4.5-.86-5.99-2.34l-3.6-3.6a2 2 0 0 1 2.83-2.82L7 15\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Handcrafted</h3><p class=\"mt-4 leading-7 text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Experienced artisans weave every product with exceptional attention to detail.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[28px] border border-[#ece6dc] bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[#edf6e8]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check text-[var(--primary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Quality Check</h3><p class=\"mt-4 leading-7 text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Every product is inspected to ensure premium finish and durability.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[28px] border border-[#ece6dc] bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[#edf6e8]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-package text-[var(--primary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11 21.73a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73z\"></path><path d=\"M12 22V12\"></path><polyline points=\"3.29 7 12 12 20.71 7\"></polyline><path d=\"m7.5 4.27 9 5.15\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Delivered</h3><p class=\"mt-4 leading-7 text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Beautifully packed and shipped to customers across US and worldwide.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white py-24 lg:py-32\"><div class=\"\n        mx-auto\n        w-full\n        max-w-[1320px]\n        px-5\n        lg:px-8\n        \n      \"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center\"><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-[var(--primary)]\">Our Values</span><h2 class=\"mt-5 font-serif text-5xl text-[var(--text)]\">What We Stand For</h2><p class=\"mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-[var(--text-muted)]\">NatureGren is built on timeless values that guide every product we create and every relationship we build.</p></div><div class=\"mt-20 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"rounded-[30px] border border-[#ece6dc] bg-[#fcfaf7] p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[#edf6e8]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-leaf text-[var(--primary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.48 19 2c1 2 2 4.18 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z\"></path><path d=\"M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Sustainability</h3><p class=\"mt-4 leading-7 text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Every decision we make is focused on reducing environmental impact through renewable materials and responsible production.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[30px] border border-[#ece6dc] bg-[#fcfaf7] p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[#edf6e8]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-hand-heart text-[var(--primary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11 14h2a2 2 0 0 0 0-4h-3c-.6 0-1.1.2-1.4.6L3 16\"></path><path d=\"m14.45 13.39 5.05-4.694C20.196 8 21 6.85 21 5.75a2.75 2.75 0 0 0-4.797-1.837.276.276 0 0 1-.406 0A2.75 2.75 0 0 0 11 5.75c0 1.2.802 2.248 1.5 2.946L16 11.95\"></path><path d=\"m2 15 6 6\"></path><path d=\"m7 20 1.6-1.4c.3-.4.8-.6 1.4-.6h4c1.1 0 2.1-.4 2.8-1.2l4.6-4.4a1 1 0 0 0-2.75-2.91\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Craftsmanship</h3><p class=\"mt-4 leading-7 text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Our artisans combine generations of skill with modern design to create products built with pride and precision.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[30px] border border-[#ece6dc] bg-[#fcfaf7] p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[#edf6e8]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-award text-[var(--primary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)]\">Premium Quality</h3><p class=\"mt-4 leading-7 text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Each NatureGren product undergoes careful inspection to ensure durability, elegance and lasting performance.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[30px] border border-[#ece6dc] bg-[#fcfaf7] p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-[#edf6e8]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users text-[var(--primary)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744\"></path><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-8 te